      "body": "Following is a series of screenshots of what i saw in the last hours of initial syncronization. I _think_ the memory hogging was worse in the beginning of syncronization.\r\nUnfortunately i haven't got any screenshots of the problem fraom the early part of syncronization when i realized something is off because almost all of my 32Gb RAM was in use and I started to see performance issues ;-)\r\n\r\n![Skærmbillede 2021-01-11 105758](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3484684/104182493-d7b36400-5410-11eb-9793-8c852d88cfc3.png)\r\n - 20 minutes to go.\r\n![Skærmbillede 2021-01-11 114854](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3484684/104182501-db46eb00-5410-11eb-9126-14a4f3062c91.png)\r\n- 6 minutes to go.\r\n![Skærmbillede 2021-01-11 120303](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3484684/104182512-deda7200-5410-11eb-8fbd-4285c5fcb672.png)\r\n - 3 minutes to go.\r\n![Skærmbillede 2021-01-11 120651](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3484684/104182533-e568e980-5410-11eb-8423-d223cc4978a5.png)\r\n -  Initial syncronization just completed.\r\n![Skærmbillede 2021-01-11 123846](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3484684/104182538-e732ad00-5410-11eb-9a66-45f877677391.png)\r\n - 4 minutes after sync. completed.\r\n![Skærmbillede 2021-01-11 123954](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3484684/104182543-e863da00-5410-11eb-9a9a-1ee89d5a8216.png)\r\n - Shutting Bitcoin Core down:\r\n![Skærmbillede 2021-01-11 125452](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3484684/104182562-f154ab80-5410-11eb-8338-49e6f3ecd841.png)\r\n - Graceful shutdown complete.\r\n![Skærmbillede 2021-01-11 125514](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3484684/104182569-f3b70580-5410-11eb-8f06-f4633870b2df.png)\r\n - \r\n![Skærmbillede 2021-01-11 125624](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3484684/104182575-f580c900-5410-11eb-8623-69674a4f3fc9.png)\r\n - Computer was rebooted.\r\n![Skærmbillede 2021-01-11 130122](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3484684/104182586-f74a8c80-5410-11eb-8541-eaf07c465b5f.png)\r\n - After reboot Bitcoin Core runs nicely and without any memory hogging going on.\r\n![Skærmbillede 2021-01-11 134918](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3484684/104185109-c9674700-5414-11eb-9e64-03dacb9a7c23.png)\r\n",
